3 LiteLLM gpt-5.3-codex

litellm_config.yaml ~/litellm_config.yaml

YAML
model_list:
  - model_name: gpt-5.3-codex
    litellm_params:
      model: github_copilot/gpt-5.3-codex
    model_info:
      mode: responses   # gpt-5.3-codex  agentic  Responses API
      # context window  LiteLLM 

  #  fallback chat/completions 
  - model_name: gpt-4o
    litellm_params:
      model: openai/gpt-4o
      #  github_copilot/gpt-4o  Copilot

general_settings:
  master_key: "sk-"   #  OpenCode

4 OpenCode LiteLLM

Bash
mkdir -p ~/.config/opencode

~/.config/opencode/opencode.json VS Code / nano

JSON
{
  "$schema": "https://opencode.ai/config.json",
  "provider": {
    "litellm": {
      "npm": "@ai-sdk/openai-compatible",
      "name": "LiteLLM (Copilot Codex)",
      "options": {
        "baseURL": "http://localhost:4000/v1",
        "apiKey": "{env:LITELLM_API_KEY}"
      },
      "models": {
        "gpt-5.3-codex": {
          "name": "GPT-5.3-Codex (GitHub Copilot via LiteLLM)",
          "limit": {
            "context": 128000,
            "output": 32000
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
